{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}My brother's not happy with the terms.{\r}

1656
01:42:47,389 --> 01:42:50,051
我们在讨论这个问题 没事的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}We'll work it out. It's nothing.{\r}

1657
01:42:58,000 --> 01:43:00,230
对不对 没事的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Right? It's nothing.{\r}

1658
01:43:06,408 --> 01:43:09,468
没事的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Yeah. Nothing.{\r}

1659
01:43:11,347 --> 01:43:13,577
尤里 你说的没错
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}You're right. Yuri, you're right.{\r}

1660
01:43:14,483 --> 01:43:16,974
上帝啊 我脑子一定出问题了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}God, I've got to get my shit together.{\r}

1661
01:43:18,087 --> 01:43:19,645
这不是我们的战争
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}This is not our fight.{\r}

1662
01:43:19,888 --> 01:43:20,877
没错
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Right.{\r}

