1679
01:44:20,215 --> 01:44:23,116
放下它 慢慢的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Step away. Slow.{\r}

1680
01:44:41,003 --> 01:44:42,937
不要 维塔利
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}No, Vit!{\r}

1681
01:44:44,873 --> 01:44:46,363
不要 维塔利
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}No! Vit!{\r}

