{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}so I was still entitled to half the diamonds.{\r}

1684
01:46:17,633 --> 01:46:19,726
如果我拿了它 我失去一些东西
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}If I took them, I was lost.{\r}

1685
01:46:19,968 --> 01:46:22,300
如果我不拿 我也是失去一些东西
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}If I left them, I was lost.{\r}

1686
01:46:30,479 --> 01:46:33,744
一场大屠杀发生了 就像维塔利所说的那样
