1691
01:46:44,626 --> 01:46:48,289
人们说“如果正义之士不行动的话邪恶就获胜了”
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}They say evil prevails when good men fail to act.{\r}

1692
01:46:48,530 --> 01:46:52,626
这句话应该是“邪恶获胜了”
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}What they ought to say is, evil prevails.{\r}

1693
01:47:06,281 --> 01:47:07,908
我现在和被上帝遗忘的…
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I now shared even more in common...{\r}

1694
01:47:08,150 --> 01:47:11,608
这个国家的统治者有了更多的相同点
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}with the leader of that country God seemed to have forsaken.{\r}

1695
01:47:11,853 --> 01:47:14,879
我们在对方看到了一些我们并不喜欢的东西
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}We saw something in each other that neither of us liked.{\r}

1696
01:47:15,123 --> 01:47:18,092
也许我们各自只是在看一面镜子
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Or maybe we were just looking in the mirror.{\r}

