1701
01:47:46,989 --> 01:47:48,923
我走私里上百万的弹药
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I've smuggled millions of rounds of ammunition,{\r}

1702
01:47:49,157 --> 01:47:50,852
但是那颗把我送到监狱里的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}and the bullet that lands me in jail...{\r}

1703
01:47:51,093 --> 01:47:53,687
确是那颗在我弟弟肋骨下的子弹
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}is found under my dead brother's rib.{\r}

1704
01:47:55,230 --> 01:47:57,027
尤里・奥洛夫
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Yuri Orlov.{\r}

1705
01:47:57,265 --> 01:48:00,098
我是美国烟酒枪械管理署的
