1706
01:48:00,335 --> 01:48:01,029
让我猜一猜
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Let me guess.{\r}

1707
01:48:01,269 --> 01:48:03,965
这一定不是关于烟和酒
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}This is not about the alcohol or the tobacco.{\r}

1708
01:48:45,614 --> 01:48:46,876
克里米亚餐馆
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Crimean Restaurant.{\r}

1709
01:48:47,115 --> 01:48:48,446
爸爸？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Papa?{\r}

1710
01:48:55,557 --> 01:48:58,253
我两个儿子都已经死了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Both my sons are dead.{\r}

1711
01:49:01,063 --> 01:49:03,657
生活中有两种悲惨的事
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}There are only two tragedies in life.{\r}

1712
01:49:03,899 --> 01:49:06,026
一种是你想要的得不到
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}One is not getting what you want.{\r}

1713
01:49:06,268 --> 01:49:07,462
另一种是你得到了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}The other is getting it.{\r}

1714
01:49:07,703 --> 01:49:08,533
这是不是你的？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Is this one of yours?{\r}

1715
01:49:08,770 --> 01:49:11,568
杰克・范伦提终于得到了他想要的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Jack Valentine finally had what he wanted.{\r}

1716
01:49:11,807 --> 01:49:16,471
真奇怪 死亡证明书上写他死于心脏衰竭
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Curiously, the death certificate says he died of heart failure.{\r}

1717
01:49:17,212 --> 01:49:19,510
伪造死亡证明书？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Falsifying a death certificate?{\r}

1718
01:49:19,748 --> 01:49:21,511
这个罪名可告不了我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}That's not gonna hold me.{\r}

1719
01:49:21,750 --> 01:49:25,345
你说得没错 和平时一样 你又说对了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}You're right. As usual, you are right.{\r}

1720
01:49:27,856 --> 01:49:31,189
你看今天的报纸了吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Have you seen today's paper? Huh?{\r}

