1725
01:49:49,244 --> 01:49:54,238
是你妻子的帮助 让我们捉到了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}It was your wife your trophy wife that led us to the prize.{\r}

1726
01:49:55,050 --> 01:49:55,641
那不是她的错
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}It's not her fault.{\r}

1727
01:49:55,884 --> 01:49:58,250
她只是比你好跟踪罢了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}She's just easier to follow than you are.{\r}

1728
01:50:00,088 --> 01:50:01,612
我可以看报纸吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}May I?{\r}

1729
01:50:01,857 --> 01:50:03,347
没问题 看吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Yeah, go ahead.{\r}

1730
01:50:28,083 --> 01:50:29,311
慢慢享受吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Enjoy it.{\r}

1731
01:50:30,051 --> 01:50:32,076
什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}What? This.{\r}

1732
01:50:32,687 --> 01:50:34,985
随你说吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Tell me I'm everything you despise.{\r}

1733
01:50:35,223 --> 01:50:37,657
说我是邪恶的化身
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}That I'm the personification of evil.{\r}

1734
01:50:37,893 --> 01:50:38,757
还有什么？
