1735
01:50:38,994 --> 01:50:43,658
应该对世界混乱的秩序负责
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Responsible for the breakdown of the fabric of society and world order.{\r}

1736
01:50:43,899 --> 01:50:46,333
创造大屠杀的人
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I'm a one-man genocide.{\r}

1737
01:50:46,568 --> 01:50:48,536
你现在想说什么就说什么吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Say everything you want to say to me now.{\r}

1738
01:50:49,271 --> 01:50:51,136
因为你已经没时间了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Because you don't have long.{\r}

1739
01:50:51,373 --> 01:50:53,034
你在注意听吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Are you paying attention?{\r}

1740
01:50:53,942 --> 01:50:56,308
还是你在做梦？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Or are you delusional?{\r}

1741
01:50:56,545 --> 01:50:59,776
你已经违反了每一条法律
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}You have broken every arms embargo written.{\r}

1742
01:51:00,015 --> 01:51:04,213
