{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}There is enough here to put you away for consecutive life sentences.{\r}

1743
01:51:04,452 --> 01:51:06,010
在你真正进监狱之前
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}You are going to spend the next ten years of your life{\r}

1744
01:51:06,254 --> 01:51:09,485
你会花十年时间
