{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I don't think you fully appreciate the seriousness...{\r}

1747
01:51:16,464 --> 01:51:18,193
这个问题的严重性
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}...of your situation.{\r}

1748
01:51:28,276 --> 01:51:31,245
我的家人不认我了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}My family has disowned me.{\r}

1749
01:51:32,514 --> 01:51:35,483
我的妻子和孩子离开了我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}My wife and son have left me.{\r}

1750
01:51:38,253 --> 01:51:39,914
我的弟弟死了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}My brother's dead.{\r}

1751
01:51:40,789 --> 01:51:42,188
相信我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Trust me.{\r}

1752
01:51:42,424 --> 01:51:46,019
我很真正认识到这个问题的严重性
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I fully appreciate the seriousness of my situation.{\r}

1753
01:51:46,261 --> 01:51:48,229
我敢对你发誓
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}But I promise you,{\r}

1754
01:51:48,463 --> 01:51:51,364
我不会在法院里呆上一秒钟
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I won't spend a single second in a courtroom.{\r}

1755
01:51:52,300 --> 01:51:53,767
你是在做梦
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}You are delusional.{\r}

1756
01:51:54,436 --> 01:51:55,926
我喜欢你杰克
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}I like you, Jack.{\r}

1757
01:51:56,872 --> 01:52:00,899
不 也许不是 但是我了解你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Well, maybe not, but I understand you.{\r}

1758
01:52:04,112 --> 01:52:06,546
让我来告诉你将会发生什么
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Let me tell you what's gonna happen.{\r}

1759
01:52:07,382 --> 01:52:10,909
这样可以让你有所准备
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}This way, you can prepare yourself.{\r}

1760
01:52:14,389 --> 01:52:15,447
好的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&}Okay.{\r}

